      "heading": null,
      "description": "Before you begin, make the Sticky Soy, Ginger &amp; Garlic Chicken Traybake batch recipe."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Boil the noodles and edamame in salted water for 5 mins, then drain and rinse under cold water."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Grate the garlic. In a bowl, whisk together the tahini, sesame oil, rice vinegar, honey, garlic and a pinch of salt. Add a splash of water and whisk again until smooth and creamy, like double cream."
