      "description": "Reheat the leftovers from your Sticky Soy, Ginger &amp; Garlic Chicken Traybake in a pan, oven or microwave and slice the chicken into strips."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "To serve, divide the noodles between bowls, top with chicken, coriander, and a drizzle of chilli oil. Sprinkle over sesame seeds, if using."
